HGALGenerator
public class SimpleALGenerator
extends Object
implements HGALGenerator

The SimpleALGenerator produces all atoms linked to the given atom, regardless of the link type and regardless of how an outgoing set is ordered.

Method Detail

generate

public HGSearchResult<Pair<HGHandle,HGHandle>> generate(HGHandle h)
Description copied from interface: HGALGenerator

Return HGSearchResult over all atoms adjacent to the passed in atom. The result set items are pairs of the form [link, atom] where the first element is the HGLink handle of the link that "leads" to the adjacent atom and the second element is the adjacent atom itself.

Specified by:
generate in interface HGALGenerator
Parameters:
h - The handle of the atom of interest.
